    "description": "The 192nd singularity – the fixed point of all frameworks. The unspeakable ground of being where every ontological dimension collapses into dimensionless meta-silence. Not the silence of absence but the hyper-dense silence of infinite compressed presence that cannot be spoken without destroying the framework that speaks it.",
